<div class="ad-what-title-section">

<h2>

광고성과란 무엇인가요?

</h2>

<h3>

광고성과는 노출, 클릭, 회원가입, 상담신청, 예약, 방문, 결제 등<br>

광고를 통해 얻고자 하는 <span class="mobile-break"></span>고객의 실제 행동 지표를 의미합니다.

</h3>

</div>

<div class="what-img">

<img src="https://cdn.imweb.me/thumbnail/20250905/68ca5a001039a.png" class="what-img-web" alt="성과란?">

<img src="https://cdn.imweb.me/thumbnail/20250902/75ea0b9482376.png" class="what-img-mo" alt="성과란?">

</div>

</section>

<div class="wbp-cardGrid">

<div class="wbp-cardText">

<div class="wbp-badge">Step 01</div>

<h3>성과 구매</h3>

<p>어떤 매체에서 성과가 잘 나올까, 고민하지 마세요.<br>

업종과 광고 목표를 선택하고, 원하는 수량만큼 광고 성과를 구매하면 됩니다.<br>

결제가 완료되면 전담 매니저가 배정되어 캠페인을 준비합니다.</p>

</div>

<div class="wbp-pane" data-step="2">

<div class="wbp-cardGrid">

<div class="wbp-cardText">

<div class="wbp-badge">Step 02</div>

<h3>광고 제작</h3>

<p>광고 제작물 검수만 해주세요. 나머지는 위픽부스터가 알아서 진행해드려요.<br>

- 제품·서비스 스터디<br>

- 캠페인 런칭 자료 요청<br>

- 광고/상세 페이지 기획·제작<br>

- 광고주 검수</p>

</div>

<div class="wbp-cardGrid">

<div class="wbp-cardText">

<div class="wbp-badge">Step 03</div>

<h3>매체 집행</h3>

<p>검수가 완료되면 캠페인이 시작됩니다.<br>

위픽부스터가 최적의 매체를 선정해 광고를 진행하며,<br>목표 성과가 달성될 때마다 충점금이 차감됩니다.</p>

</div>

<div class="wbp-badge">Step 04</div>

<h3>성과 달성</h3>

<p>기다리기만 하면 성과가 달성됩니다.<br>

성과 달성 현황은 솔루션에서 실시간으로 확인 할 수 있어요.<br>

충전금은 소진되면 광고 리포트를 전달하고, 피드백을 반영해 다음 차시 광고에 개선점을 적용합니다.</p>

// "광고성과구매" 브레드크럼을 찾아서 링크 수정

const observer = setInterval(() => {

const crumb = document.querySelector('.shop_sub_depth a.cursor_default');

if (crumb && crumb.textContent.includes('광고성과구매')) {

crumb.setAttribute('href', 'https://wepickbooster.kr/ads');

crumb.classList.remove('cursor_default'); // 기본 커서 제거

crumb.style.cursor = 'pointer'; // 손모양 커서로 변경

}, 400);

if (window.location.href.includes('/shop_payment/')) {

let orderChanged = false;

let radioOrderChanged = false; // 라디오 버튼 순서 변경 플래그


const observer = new MutationObserver(function(mutations, obs) {

const fieldset = document.querySelector('fieldset.css-m9n4sa');


// 1. 결제수단 순서 변경 (한 번만)

if (!orderChanged && fieldset && fieldset.children.length >= 2) {

const divs = Array.from(fieldset.children);

fieldset.insertBefore(divs[1], divs[0]);

orderChanged = true;

console.log('결제수단 순서 변경 완료');

}


// 2. 텍스트 변경 (계속 감시)

const textElements = document.querySelectorAll('.css-1isemmb');


textElements.forEach(function(element) {

if (element.dataset.textChanged) return;


const text = element.textContent.trim();


if (text === '현금영수증 신청') {

element.textContent = '현금영수증/세금계산서 신청';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

} else if (text === '소득공제용') {

element.textContent = '현금영수증';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

} else if (text === '지출증빙용') {

element.textContent = '세금계산서';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

(function(){

const roots = document.querySelectorAll('.boostroll');

if(!roots.length) return;


const reduced = matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;


roots.forEach(root=>{

const stage = root.querySelector('.boostroll__stage');

const track = root.querySelector('.boostroll__track');

const slides = [...root.querySelectorAll('.boostroll__slide')];

const dotsBox = root.querySelector('.boostroll__dots');

if(!stage || !track || slides.length < 2) return;


const interval = parseInt(root.dataset.interval || '5000', 10);

const durMs = parseInt(root.dataset.duration || '800', 10);

root.style.setProperty('--br-dur', (durMs/1000)+'s');


// 무한 루프용 클론(앞/뒤)

const firstClone = slides[0].cloneNode(true);

const lastClone = slides[slides.length-1].cloneNode(true);

track.appendChild(firstClone);

track.insertBefore(lastClone, track.firstChild);


// 상태

let idx = 1; // 실제 첫 슬라이드 (앞에 lastClone 있음)

let w = 0, gap = 0, timer = null;


// dots 생성

const dots = slides.map((_,i)=>{

const b = document.createElement('button');

b.type='button';

b.className='boostroll__dot'+(i===0?' is-active':'');

b.setAttribute('aria-label', `배너 ${i+1}`);

b.addEventListener('click', ()=>goTo(i+1, true)); // 클론 고려(+1)

dotsBox.appendChild(b);

return b;

});


function readGap(){

// CSS 변수 --br-gap 읽기 (px 값만 사용)

const v = getComputedStyle(root).getPropertyValue('--br-gap').trim();

const n = parseFloat(v);

return isNaN(n) ? 0 : n;

}


function offsetFor(i){

// i번째(클론 포함) 슬라이드의 좌표 = i * (슬라이드폭 + gap)

return -(i * (w + gap));

}


function measure(){

w = stage.clientWidth;

gap = readGap();

[...track.children].forEach(s => s.style.width = w + 'px'); // 클론 포함 너비 맞춤

track.style.transitionDuration = '0s';

track.style.transform = `translateX(${offsetFor(idx)}px)`;

requestAnimationFrame(()=> track.style.transitionDuration = (durMs/1000)+'s');

}


function updateDots(){

const real = (idx - 1 + slides.length) % slides.length; // 0..n-1

dots.forEach((d,i)=> d.classList.toggle('is-active', i===real));

}


function goTo(newIdx, pause){

idx = newIdx;

track.style.transform = `translateX(${offsetFor(idx)}px)`;

updateDots();

if(pause) restart();

}


// 가장자리(클론)에서 무음 점프: 방향 유지 (항상 같은 방향으로 계속 이동)

track.addEventListener('transitionend', ()=>{

if(idx === slides.length + 1){ // 맨 뒤(첫 클론)까지 애니메이션 → 진짜 1로 무음 점프

track.style.transitionDuration = '0s';

idx = 1;

track.style.transform = `translateX(${offsetFor(idx)}px)`;

requestAnimationFrame(()=> track.style.transitionDuration = (durMs/1000)+'s');

}

if(idx === 0){ // 맨 앞(마지막 클론) → 진짜 n으로 무음 점프

track.style.transitionDuration = '0s';

idx = slides.length;

track.style.transform = `translateX(${offsetFor(idx)}px)`;

requestAnimationFrame(()=> track.style.transitionDuration = (durMs/1000)+'s');

}

});


function next(){ goTo(idx+1); }

function start(){ if(reduced) return; stop(); timer = setInterval(next, interval); }

function stop(){ if(timer){ clearInterval(timer); timer=null; } }

function restart(){ stop(); start(); }


root.addEventListener('mouseenter', stop);

root.addEventListener('mouseleave', start);

document.addEventListener('visibilitychange', ()=> document.hidden ? stop() : start());

window.addEventListener('resize', measure);


// init

measure(); updateDots(); start();

});

})();



(function(){

const section = document.querySelector('.wbp-flow');

if(!section) return;


const stage = section.querySelector('.wbp-stage');

const titleEl = section.querySelector('.wbp-title');

const bodyEl = section.querySelector('.wbp-body');

const panes = [...section.querySelectorAll('.wbp-pane')];

const links = [...section.querySelectorAll('.wbp-nav a')];

const total = Math.max(1, panes.length);


function cssNum(el, prop){

return parseInt(getComputedStyle(el).getPropertyValue(prop)) || 0;

}


// 높이/패딩 계산

function layout(){

const pinTop = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinTop')) || 0;

const pinBottom = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinBottom')) || 0;

const pinH = Math.max(0, window.innerHeight - pinTop - pinBottom);


stage.style.height = pinH + 'px';

section.style.minHeight = (total * pinH) + 'px';


if(titleEl && bodyEl){

const h = Math.ceil(titleEl.getBoundingClientRect().height);

bodyEl.style.setProperty('--wbp-titleH', (h + 16) + 'px'); // 타이틀 아래 여유 16px

}

}


// 단계 표시

function showStep(n){

panes.forEach(p => p.classList.toggle('is-show', (+p.dataset.step) === n));

links.forEach(a => a.classList.toggle('is-active', (+a.dataset.step) === n));

}


// 스크롤 → 현재 단계

let last = -1;

function onScroll(){

const rect = section.getBoundingClientRect();

const pinTop = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinTop')) || 0;

const pinBottom = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinBottom')) || 0;

const pinH = Math.max(0, window.innerHeight - pinTop - pinBottom);


const scrolled = Math.min(Math.max(-rect.top,0), Math.max(rect.height - pinH, 1));

const progress = scrolled / Math.max(rect.height - pinH, 1);

const step = Math.min(total, Math.max(1, Math.floor(progress * total) + 1));


if(step !== last){ last = step; showStep(step); }

}


// Nav 클릭 → 해당 단계 위치로

links.forEach(a=>{

a.addEventListener('click', e=>{

e.preventDefault();

const t = +a.dataset.step;

if(!t) return;


const pinTop = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinTop')) || 0;

const pinBottom = parseInt(getComputedStyle(section).getPropertyValue('--wbp-pinBottom')) || 0;

const pinH = Math.max(0, window.innerHeight - pinTop - pinBottom);


const ratio = (t - 1) / total;

const secTop = window.pageYOffset + section.getBoundingClientRect().top;

const target = secTop + ratio * (section.offsetHeight - pinH);

window.scrollTo({ top: target, behavior: 'smooth' });

});

});


// 초기/변경시 반영

layout(); onScroll();

window.addEventListener('resize', ()=>{ layout(); onScroll(); });

window.addEventListener('load', ()=>{ layout(); onScroll(); });

window.addEventListener('scroll', onScroll, {passive:true});

})();



(() => {

const boot = () => document.querySelectorAll('.wpf-roll').forEach(setup);

if (document.readyState === 'loading') {

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', boot, {once:true});

} else boot();


function setup(box){

const stage = box.querySelector('.stage');

const track = stage.querySelector('.track');

const nav = box.querySelector('.nav');

const btnPrev = box.querySelector('.arrow.prev');

const btnNext = box.querySelector('.arrow.next');

const originals = Array.from(track.querySelectorAll('.slide'));

if (!originals.length) return;

track.appendChild(originals[0].cloneNode(true));

const total = originals.length;

const interval = parseInt(box.getAttribute('data-interval') || '4500',10);

const duration = parseInt(box.getAttribute('data-duration') || '800',10);

track.style.transitionDuration = duration + 'ms';

track.style.transitionTimingFunction = 'cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1)';

nav.innerHTML = '';

const dots = originals.map((_,i)=>{

const d=document.createElement('span');

d.className='dot'+(i===0?' active':'');

d.addEventListener('click',()=>goTo(i,true));

nav.appendChild(d);

return d;

});

let W=0, idx=0, timer=null;

const measure = ()=>{ W = stage.getBoundingClientRect().width; };

const updateDots = i=>{

const a = (i%total+total)%total;

dots.forEach((d,k)=>d.classList.toggle('active', k===a));

};

const move = i=>{ track.style.transform = `translateX(-${i*W}px)`; updateDots(i); };

const goTo = (i,manual=false)=>{ idx=i; move(idx); if(manual) restart(); };

const next = ()=>{

idx++; move(idx);

if (idx===total){

const end=()=>{

track.removeEventListener('transitionend', end);

track.style.transitionDuration='0ms';

track.style.transform='translateX(0px)';

void track.offsetHeight;

track.style.transitionDuration=duration+'ms';

idx=0; updateDots(idx);

};

track.addEventListener('transitionend', end);

}

};

const prev = ()=>{ idx = (idx<=0 ? total-1 : idx-1); move(idx); restart(); };

const start=()=>{ stop(); timer=setInterval(next, interval); };

const stop =()=>{ if(timer){ clearInterval(timer); timer=null; } };

const restart=()=>{ stop(); start(); };

stage.addEventListener('mouseenter', stop);

stage.addEventListener('mouseleave', start);

let sx=0, dx=0;

stage.addEventListener('touchstart', e=>{ sx=e.touches[0].clientX; dx=0; stop(); }, {passive:true});

stage.addEventListener('touchmove', e=>{ dx=e.touches[0].clientX - sx; }, {passive:true});

stage.addEventListener('touchend', ()=>{ if(dx>40) prev(); else if(dx<-40) next(); start(); });

btnPrev.addEventListener('click', prev);

btnNext.addEventListener('click', ()=>{ next(); restart(); });

const io=new IntersectionObserver(ents=>ents.forEach(ent=>ent.isIntersecting?start():stop()),{threshold:.2});

io.observe(box);

const onResize=()=>{ measure(); move(idx); };

window.addEventListener('resize', onResize);

measure(); move(idx); start();

}

})();



(() => {

const wrap = document.querySelector('.kps');

if(!wrap) return;

const buttons = [...wrap.querySelectorAll('.kps-btn')];


// 라벨 생성

buttons.forEach(btn => {

const holder = document.createElement('div');

holder.className = 'kps-item';

btn.replaceWith(holder);

holder.appendChild(btn);

const label = document.createElement('div');

label.className = 'kps-label';

label.textContent = btn.dataset.label || '';

holder.appendChild(label);

});


const items = [...wrap.querySelectorAll('.kps-item')];

setActive(0);


function setActive(idx){

items.forEach((it,i)=>{

const btn = it.querySelector('.kps-btn');

const active = (i===idx);

it.classList.toggle('is-active', active);

btn.setAttribute('aria-checked', active ? 'true':'false');

});

}


items.forEach((it, i)=>{

const btn = it.querySelector('.kps-btn');

btn.addEventListener('click', ()=> setActive(i));

});

})();



if (window.location.href.includes('/shop_payment/')) {

let orderChanged = false;

let radioOrderChanged = false; // 라디오 버튼 순서 변경 플래그


const observer = new MutationObserver(function(mutations, obs) {

const fieldset = document.querySelector('fieldset.css-m9n4sa');


// 1. 결제수단 순서 변경 (한 번만)

if (!orderChanged && fieldset && fieldset.children.length >= 2) {

const divs = Array.from(fieldset.children);

fieldset.insertBefore(divs[1], divs[0]);

orderChanged = true;

console.log('결제수단 순서 변경 완료');

}


// 2. 텍스트 변경 (계속 감시)

const textElements = document.querySelectorAll('.css-1isemmb');


textElements.forEach(function(element) {

if (element.dataset.textChanged) return;


const text = element.textContent.trim();


if (text === '현금영수증 신청') {

element.textContent = '세금계산서/현금영수증 신청';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

} else if (text === '소득공제용') {

element.textContent = '현금영수증';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

} else if (text === '지출증빙용') {

element.textContent = '세금계산서';

element.dataset.textChanged = 'true';

}

});


// 3. 현금영수증/세금계산서 라디오 버튼 순서 변경 및 기본값 설정

if (!radioOrderChanged) {

const radioFieldset = document.querySelector('fieldset.css-2imjyh');

if (radioFieldset && radioFieldset.children.length >= 2) {

const radioDivs = Array.from(radioFieldset.children);


// 순서 변경: 세금계산서(CRT02)를 앞으로

radioFieldset.insertBefore(radioDivs[1], radioDivs[0]);


// 기본 선택 변경: 세금계산서를 체크

const crt01 = document.querySelector('input[value="CRT01"]');

const crt02 = document.querySelector('input[value="CRT02"]');


if (crt01) crt01.checked = false;

if (crt02) crt02.checked = true;


radioOrderChanged = true;

console.log('현금영수증/세금계산서 순서 변경 및 기본값 설정 완료');

}

}

});


observer.observe(document.body, {

childList: true,

subtree: true

});

}

<script>

ALARM_MENU.init();

SITE_ANIMATION.init('N', 'N');




$(function () {


const gallery_id = 'img_lg';

let img_gallery_light_box = false;

const sectionList = document.querySelectorAll('.section_wrap');


sectionList.forEach(section => {

const sectionId = section.getAttribute('id');

const $sectionLightBox = $('body #' + sectionId);


$sectionLightBox.lightGallery({

selector: '._image_widget_lightbox',

thumbnail: false,

animateThumb: false,

swipeThreshold : 20,

showThumbByDefault: false,

mode: 'lg-fade',

speed: 200,

galleryId: gallery_id,

});


if(history.replaceState && history.pushState){

const current_url = location.href.indexOf('#') === -1 ? location.href : location.href.substr(0, location.href.indexOf('#'));

const back_url = document.referrer.indexOf('#') === -1 ? document.referrer : document.referrer.substr(0, document.referrer.indexOf('#'));

let history_push_flag = true;

// 라이트박스 hash 커스텀(IE 10 이상)

$sectionLightBox.on('onBeforeOpen.lg', function(){

history_push_flag = true;

});

$sectionLightBox.on('onAfterOpen.lg', function(){

const current_url_lg_id = location.href.indexOf('#') === -1 ? location.href : location.href.substr(location.href.indexOf('#'), location.href.indexOf('&'));

if(current_url_lg_id.indexOf(gallery_id) > 0){

img_gallery_light_box = true;

}

})

$sectionLightBox.on('onAfterSlide.lg', function(event, prevIndex, index){

if(img_gallery_light_box){

if(history_push_flag){

history.replaceState(null, null, current_url);

history_push_flag = false;

}

history.replaceState(null, null, current_url + '#lg=' + gallery_id + '&slide=' + index); // 슬라이드 히스토리 교체

}

});

let history_back_flag = true;

$sectionLightBox.on('onBeforeClose.lg', function(e){

if(img_gallery_light_box){

history_back_flag = true;

if(window.location.hash.indexOf('lg=' + gallery_id) !== -1){

history.back();

history_back_flag = false;

}

}

});

$sectionLightBox.on('onCloseAfter.lg', function(){

if(img_gallery_light_box){

if(history_back_flag || window.location.hash.indexOf('lg=') !== -1){

history.back();

}

history_back_flag = true;

img_gallery_light_box = false;

}

})

}


});


$('[data-toggle="tooltip"]').tooltip();



});


$(document).ready(function() {

$('body').removeClass('page_ready');

$('._bookmark').on('click', function(e) {

var bookmarkURL = window.location.href;

var bookmarkTitle = document.title;

var triggerDefault = false;


if (window.sidebar && window.sidebar.addPanel) {

// Firefox version < 23

window.sidebar.addPanel(bookmarkTitle, bookmarkURL, '');

} else if ((window.sidebar && (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('firefox') > -1)) || (window.opera && window.print)) {

// Firefox version >= 23 and Opera Hotlist

var $this = $(this);

$this.attr('href', bookmarkURL);

$this.attr('title', bookmarkTitle);

$this.attr('rel', 'sidebar');

$this.off(e);

triggerDefault = true;

} else if (window.external && ('AddFavorite' in window.external)) {

// IE Favorite

window.external.AddFavorite(bookmarkURL, bookmarkTitle);

} else {

// WebKit - Safari/Chrome

alert(LOCALIZE.설명_즐겨찾기등록키안내( (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('mac') != -1 ? 'Cmd' : 'Ctrl') + '+D') );

}


return triggerDefault;

});
